0.1.1:
- Can now edit slides while slides are running
- Alerts now show in slide
- Fixed some animations on the web panel
- Fixed some injected font sizes being affected by external websites css
- Github action now builds to a .zip instead of .tar.gz
- Fixed rendering bugs in chrome
- Limited text length
- Made Update and Delete buttons more obvious
- Ads, trackers and most cookie popups are now blocked
- Cleaned up code a bit
- Added a lot of comments
- Added more error handling
- Added error reporting
- Apps now load, but do not run
- You *can* technically add / remove apps on the web panel, but they do not do anything, and you cannot edit them